Write a program to print the below pattern 
1 
2 2 
3  3  3     
4  4   4   4 

CODE: 
public class NumberPattern {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 4;   // change value for testing

        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {
                System.out.print(i + " ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
